        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Reservation Management</h2>
        <p>Customize table availability, manage bookings, and accept reservations online.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white shadow rounded">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Social Media Integration</h2>
        <p>Connect your Facebook, Instagram, and other channels to your website.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white shadow rounded">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">SEO Optimization</h2>
        <p>Improve your visibility on Google for “restaurants near me.”</p>
      </div>
    </div>

